  "texts": [
    "Athletic events are one of the few instances where hundreds of thousands of people may gather together on a weekly basis to cheer for their favorite team or player.",
    "In addition to the sheer number of spectators, there are millions of youth around the world that participate in some form of organized or recreational sports activities.",
    "Hence, our group has been working to leverage sports to support learning and creating with AI, and similarly, to help youth see how they can use AI/ML to improve their athletic performance.",
    "In particular, we have spent the past few years engaging in sports-related AI/ML learning in physical education classes, computer science/coding classes, after-school clubs, multi-week summer camps, STEM festivals, professional sports events, youth sports practices, local community centers, and more (see Figure 4).",
    "At a high level, these experiences introduce youth to different sports technologies and challenge them to create sports technologies of their own."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}